{"word":"μηκέτι","slug":"μηκέτι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μηϰέτι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μή\">μή</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔτι\">ἔτι</a></el> (formed like <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐκέτι\">οὐκέτι</a></el>)] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b>no longer, not from now on <a href='B:470 21:19'>Mt 21:19</a>; <a href='B:480 1:45'>Mk 1:45</a>; <a href='B:500 5:14'>J 5:14</a>; <a href='B:510 4:17'>Ac 4:17</a>; <a href='B:510 13:34'>13:34</a>; <a href='B:520 6:6'>Ro 6:6</a>; <a href='B:540 5:15'>2 Cor 5:15</a>; <a href='B:560 4:14'>Eph 4:14</a>; <a href='B:590 3:1'>1 Th 3:1</a>; <a href='B:610 5:23'>1 Ti 5:23</a>; <a href='B:670 4:2'>1 Pt 4:2</a>;</b> after a <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ neg.\">neg.</a> <b>any longer <a href='B:480 11:14'>Mk 11:14</a>; <a href='B:510 25:24'>Ac 25:24</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:μηθέν\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:μῆκος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}